  TALLON ZEK DEAD!<BR>
<br>
<img src="http://www.furysedge.com/news/030904/Tallon.jpg" style="border:0;" ><br>
<br>What else is there to say? We straight up owned him, check out the cool stuff he gave us! <br>

<br>
Grats Jedani on: <br>
 <img src="http://www.furysedge.com/news/030904/Tallonboots.jpg" style="border:0;" ><br>
<br>
